  "description": {
    "canonical": "The Thalys played a ceremonial role in the Zariman harvest festival, and was intended to reap the first fruits of Tau. Now twisted from this purpose, it plants Void shards in enemy flesh instead. Each new shard planted causes existing shards to inflict damage on their hosts.",
    "display": "（英文：THALYS）大力士曾在扎里曼收获节中扮演仪式性的角色，原本用来收获 Tau 星系的最初成果。而如今，它的用途已被扭曲，转而在敌人的肉体中播种虚空碎片。每种下一块新碎片，现有的碎片便会对宿主造成伤害。",
    "localizationStatus": "official-zh"
  },
